Report written to `.hex-skills/runtime-artifacts/runs/standalone-641-20260409120800/audit-report/ln-641--full-codebase-pattern-analysis.md`

**10 patterns analyzed across 48 files. 97 issues found: 7 CRITICAL, 31 HIGH, 40 MEDIUM, 19 LOW.**

### Per-Pattern Scores

| Pattern | Score | Verdict |
|---------|-------|---------|
| Strategy (AIM dispatch) | **7.0** | Strongest pattern — textbook dispatch table |
| State Machine (account lifecycle) | **7.3** | Solid enum usage, good tests, but not persisted live |
| Circuit Breaker | **6.8** | Correct math, L6 stub + no alerting |
| Vault / Encryption | **6.8** | Correct crypto, operational gaps (rotation, atomicity) |
